00:20:09.080 --> 00:20:12.000
At home.
we settle down to a new life.

150
00:20:49.800 --> 00:20:52.360
All parents would like
their children

151
00:20:52.360 --> 00:20:55.600
to grow up in peace
and tranquillity.

152
00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:04.560
But for most of this century.

153
00:21:04.560 --> 00:21:06.200
the people of this world

154
00:21:06.200 --> 00:21:10.320
have had to live through bewildering
changes and upheavals.

155
00:21:15.080 --> 00:21:16.760
Darling Grannie.

156
00:21:16.760 --> 00:21:19.040
we have been very busy
knitting lately.

157
00:21:20.760 --> 00:21:23.280
We made a blanket for
the evacuees.

158
00:21:23.280 --> 00:21:25.360
also some jumpers and stockings.

159
