00:21:32.520 --> 00:21:35.240
Let us hope that this war
will not last long.

162
00:22:12.120 --> 00:22:15.200
Some cultures believe
a long life brings wisdom.

163
00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:19.240
I'd like to think so.

164
00:22:23.040 --> 00:22:24.880
Perhaps part of that wisdom

165
00:22:24.880 --> 00:22:28.640
is to recognise some
of life's baffling paradoxes.

166
00:22:36.920 --> 00:22:43.480
Such as the way human beings
have a huge propensity for good

167
00:22:43.480 --> 00:22:48.520
and yet a capacity for evil.

168
00:22:53.960 --> 00:22:56.680
