210
00:26:05.800 --> 00:26:09.760
Your very loving granddaughter.
Lilibet.

211
00:26:15.840 --> 00:26:18.400
It is not enough
simply to do our jobs.

212
00:26:20.680 --> 00:26:23.640
Service demands sacrifice.

213
