of our steadfastness.

237
00:29:08.600 --> 00:29:12.480
He never wavered in his faith
that. with God's help.

238
00:29:12.480 --> 00:29:15.560
the cause of freedom would prevail.

239
00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:27.320
